<div id="Idea_4083"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4083-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4083">Enforce the Logan  Act &nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/9481-4049">stevensje</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Our American citizens joining  secret,behind closed door groups making policy, etc.is against our law. They meet with foreign people...leaders, royals, corporate CEOs, bankers, etc. in our name. No journalists are allowed to know what they talk about or who is at the meetings. <br/><br/>This is a law not enforced by our government because many of them belong to these groups. By ignoring them it has given them great power. It should not matter who it is...since no one is above the law. Seems they are today. </div>
